#: Module.php:2236
msgid "The file .htaccess is not writable, so the rule for types \"{types}\" set below could not be applied. Add the following lines manually in the file .htaccess at the root of Omeka, just after \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"
msgstr "N'haller ket skrivañ war ar restr .htaccess, setu perak n'hall ket ar reolenn evit an doareoù \"{types}\" termenet a-is bezañ lakaet e pleustr. Ouzhpennit an linennoù da-heul gant an dorn er restr .htaccess e gwrizienn Omeka, just goude \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"

#: Module.php:2248
msgid "No .htaccess rule is set to protect files. To control access to files, add the following lines in the file .htaccess at the root of Omeka, just after \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"
msgstr "N'eus reolenn .htaccess ebet lakaet evit gwareziñ ar restroù. Evit kontrollañ an digor d'ar restroù, ouzhpennit al linennoù da-heul er restr .htaccess e gwrizienn Omeka, just goude \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"

#: Module.php:2300
msgid "The file .htaccess is not writable. Add the following lines manually in the file .htaccess at the root of Omeka, just after \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"
msgstr "N'haller ket skrivañ war ar restr .htaccess. Ouzhpennit an linennoù da-heul gant an dorn er restr .htaccess e gwrizienn Omeka, just goude \"RewriteEngine On\":{line_break}{rule}"

#: Module.php:2310
